[30;1m7 | [0m[35m    A finite-state machine (FSM) or finite-state automaton (FSA, plural: automata), finite automaton[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35m    or simply a state machine, is a mathematical model of computation.[0m
[30;1m9 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35m    It is an abstract machine that can be in exactly one of a finite number of states at any given t[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35m    The FSM can change from one state to another in response to some inputs;[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35m    the change from one state to another is called a transition.[0m

[30;1m5 | [0m[35m############[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35mLong-polling is a technology that allows a Telegram server to send updates in case[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35mwhen you don't have dedicated IP address or port to receive webhooks for example[0m
[30;1m9 | [0m[35mon a developer machine.[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35mTo use long-polling mode you should use :meth:`aiogram.dispatcher.dispatcher.Dispatcher.start_pollin[0m
